dc_description_s: This data represent school districts for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2020. [This polygon data layer displays the geographic area of the School Distrcits within Washburn County, Wisconsin. The school district boundaries are displayed per the school district classification within the Washburn County taxroll.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://co.washburn.wi.us/gis-data-downloads/
